thread.title: BRIEF-Nemetschek FY 2017 EBITDA Up At EUR 108 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Nemetschek FY 2017 EBITDA Up At EUR 108 Mln
text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - NEMETSCHEK SE:
* DGAP-NEWS: NEMETSCHEK SE: STRONG DOUBLE-DIGIT REVENUE GROWTH AND OVER-PROPORTIONAL INCREASE IN EARNINGS IN 2017
* FY EBITDA 108 MILLION EUR VERSUS 88 MILLION EUR YEAR AGO * FY CONSIDERABLE RISE IN GROUP REVENUE TO EUR 395.6 MILLION (+17.3%) DESPITE NEGATIVE CURRENCY EFFECTS
* FOR 2018, AS RESULT OF US TAX REFORM, TAX RATE IN GROUP EXPECTED TO BE AROUND 3 PP LOWER THAN INITIALLY ANTICIPATED: 26% TO 28% Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
